00086 #include <glm/mat4x4.hpp> // glm::mat4
00087 #include <glm/gtc/matrix_transform.hpp> // glm::translate, glm::rotate, glm::scale, glm::perspective
00088 #include <glm/gtc/type_ptr.hpp> // glm::value_ptr
00089 void func(GLuint LocationMVP, float Translate, glm::vec2 const & Rotate)
00090 {
00091         glm::mat4 Projection = glm::perspective(45.0f, 4.0f / 3.0f, 0.1f, 100.f);
00092         glm::mat4 ViewTranslate = glm::translate(glm::mat4(1.0f), glm::vec3(0.0f, 0.0f, -Translate));
00093         glm::mat4 ViewRotateX = glm::rotate(ViewTranslate, Rotate.y, glm::vec3(-1.0f, 0.0f, 0.0f));
00094         glm::mat4 View = glm::rotate(ViewRotateX, Rotate.x, glm::vec3(0.0f, 1.0f, 0.0f));
00095         glm::mat4 Model = glm::scale(glm::mat4(1.0f), glm::vec3(0.5f));
00096         glm::mat4 MVP = Projection * View * Model;
00097         glUniformMatrix4fv(LocationMVP, 1, GL_FALSE, glm::value_ptr(MVP));
00098 }
